OL,3,CThe refugees being separated under UK
OL,4,Cfamily reunion visa rules
OL,6,FThe Alrfaai family are trying to build
OL,7,Fa new life together in Glasgow. After
OL,8,Fescaping the war in Syria, they were
OL,9,Fgranted asylum in Scotland three years
OL,10,Fago.
OL,12,FBut one person is missing, their
OL,13,Feldest son Mohammed, 21, is now facing
OL,14,Fdeportation to Africa.
OL,16,F"The whole family is suffering. His
OL,17,Fmum and his sisters are all struggling
OL,18,Fto comprehend the fact that he might
OL,19,Fbe moved to Rwanda," Mohammed's father
OL,20,FHisham Alrfaai told ITV News.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G1/12
