OL,3,CThe refugees being separated under UK
OL,4,Cfamily reunion visa rules
OL,6,F"It doesn't make sense - the Home
OL,7,FOffice knows that his whole family's
OL,8,Fhere. So instead of reuniting him with
OL,9,Fthem, they are separating him, sending
OL,10,Fhim somewhere else. Rwanda. What does
OL,11,Fhe have to do? There is just nothing."
OL,13,FBecause he's over 18, Mohammed
OL,14,Fcouldn't get a family reunion visa to
OL,15,Fjoin his family.
OL,17,FIn desperation, he said he crossed the
OL,18,Fchannel illegally on a small boat in
OL,19,F2022.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/12
