OL,6,FSpeaking from a detention centre near
OL,7,FGatwick, he told ITV News he's close
OL,8,Fto having a mental breakdown,
OL,9,Ftraumatised by what's now happening.
OL,11,F"They said they're going to deport me,
OL,12,Fthey said my asylum claim is not being
OL,13,Faccepted, but I don't understand
OL,14,Fwhy... they said you came here through
OL,15,Fthe backdoor, but I don't know what
OL,16,Fother door, they don't have any other
OL,17,Fdoors. I don't understand," Mohammed
OL,18,FAlrfaai said.
