OL,4,Cfamily reunion visa rules
OL,6,FFamily reunion visas are one of the
OL,7,Fonly safe routes to the UK for
OL,8,Frefugees, but charities warn there's a
OL,9,Fbacklog of applications, many wait
OL,10,Fmuch longer than the Home Office's
OL,11,Ftarget of 12 weeks, while others
OL,12,Faren't eligible to apply at all, due
OL,13,Fto their age for example.
OL,15,FCharities warn that a lack of safe and
OL,16,Flegal routes is pushing vulnerable
OL,17,Ffamilies into the hands of people
OL,18,Fsmuggling gangs.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/12
