OL,6,FPhilippa Kemp is a family
OL,7,Fpsychotherapist who works with
OL,8,Frefugees across Yorkshire.
OL,10,FFor the last three years, she's been
OL,11,Fsupporting Afghan children who are
OL,12,Fdesperate to find a way to bring close
OL,13,Ffamily members to the UK.
OL,15,F"As the time has passed I've just seen
OL,16,Fthem crumble and become more
OL,17,Fdepressed, they've got both physical
OL,18,Fand mental health issues," she said.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G8/12
